  <div class="container narrow" style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:48px 24px;">
    <p style="font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#C8102E; margin-bottom:10px;">Tier 3 service-specific pages for Rancho Cucamonga</p>
